{"text_id":217782,"tokens":["A"," parallel","-","in","-","time"," algorithm"," based"," on"," an"," augmented"," Lagrangian"," approach"," is"," proposed"," to"," solve"," four","-","dimensional"," variational"," (","4","D","-","Var",")"," data"," assimilation"," problems","."," The"," assimilation"," window"," is"," divided"," into"," multiple"," sub","-","intervals"," that"," allows"," to"," paralle","lize"," cost"," function"," and"," gradient"," computations","."," Solution"," continuity"," equations"," across"," interval"," boundaries"," are"," added"," as"," constraints","."," The"," augmented"," Lagrangian"," approach"," leads"," to"," a"," different"," formulation"," of"," the"," variational"," data"," assimilation"," problem"," than"," weakly"," constrained"," ","4","D","-","Var","."," A"," combination"," of"," serial"," and"," parallel"," ","4","D","-","Vars"," to"," increase"," performance"," is"," also"," explored","."," The"," methodology"," is"," illustrated"," on"," data"," assimilation"," problems"," with"," Lorenz","-","9","6"," and"," the"," shallow"," water"," models","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"human","label":0}